Class Project

java.lang.Object
BTO_System.Project
public class Project extends Object
Represents a BTO (Build-To-Order) housing project managed by the Housing Development Board. This class encapsulates all information about a BTO project including its location, available flat types, unit counts, application dates, and associated users.
